import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'
const Navbar = () => {
    return ( <
        header >
        <
        div className = "container" >
        <
        Link to = "/" >
        <
        h1 > Workout BUBDY < /h1> <
        /Link> <
        /div> <
        /header>
    )
}
export default Navbar
